## Additional Disclaimer

This project provides system configuration files and guides that modify critical
system settings. While tested on specific hardware, the maintainers cannot
guarantee compatibility with all systems.

**Use at your own risk. Always back up your system before applying configurations.**

The maintainers are not responsible for:
- System instability or crashes
- Data loss
- Hardware damage
- Any other issues arising from use of these configurations

By using this software, you acknowledge that you understand the risks involved
in modifying system configurations and accept full responsibility for any
consequences.
